# Krypton Tech Stack

- Frontend: TanStack Start + React 19 + Tailwind (NOT Next.js)
- Solana: Anchor (Rust) — krypton_core + adapters
- Signing: Ika dWallet MPC (not confidential balances)
- Orchestrator: TypeScript + OpenRouter
- Simulation: Rust krypton-sim-rs
- RPC: Helius; Oracles: Pyth; Storage: Arweave
